      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REBORN DESTINY (3) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from three starts. In the money last time at this track (23.19) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2 length third. Rates on top and should go close. MISS ELPHABA (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 23.05 beating Imperator. Sure to measure up. SUPER STORM (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Maitland in a handy 22.47 beating His Fernando. Expecting another bold showing. HOOKED ON HOPE (8) is a last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
